		<description><![CDATA[Today we want you to take a moment and enjoy a new dramatic comedy parody series we discovered. It&#8217;s called Got 2 B Real. Check This Out it&#8217;s better than Basketball Wives with Female Celebrities &#8211; Throwin Shade, Pew Pewww It almost kills me when at 3:52 Rihanna says: &#8220;This is the time where we [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="aligncenter" src="http://badgals-radio.com/wp-content/uploads/HLIC/b036bee6adc7970ae1b255349eee0cfb.jpg" alt="" width="480" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Today we want you to take a moment and enjoy a new dramatic comedy parody series we discovered. <strong>It&#8217;s called<a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/LaBelleOfTheBall2/videos" target="_blank"> Got 2 B Real</a>.</strong> Check This Out it&#8217;s better than Basketball Wives with Female Celebrities &#8211; Throwin Shade, Pew Pewww</p>
<p><object width="500" height="284" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/d01MF9WdsC0?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed width="500" height="284" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/d01MF9WdsC0?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" allowFullScreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" /></object></p>
<p>It almost kills me when at 3:52 Rihanna says:</p>
<blockquote><p><em><strong>&#8220;This is the time where we ask her for Receipt because I&#8217;m not even sure Beyonce has the right to vote</strong>&#8220;</em></p></blockquote>
<p style="text-align: justify;">NOOOOOOOOO NOOOOOOOOOOOOO Jesus NOOO.. Damn that was a big ass coconut Rih-Rih.  Then just moments later Dionne says:</p>
<blockquote><p><strong><em>&#8220;Beyonce Damn Girl, your fans is like jehovas&#8217; witnesses&#8217; you can&#8217;t get they ass to go away&#8221;..</em></strong></p></blockquote>
<p style="text-align: justify;">my my my I need to wipe my face because I&#8217;m cryin. The next receipt is requested by Aretha from Patty &#8211; Yes she does. it&#8217;s more than anyone can watch without running it back several times.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Another of my most favorite shade moments comes at 6:51 when Rih-Rih mentions Mariahs&#8217; recent Jennie Craig commercials.  Mariah replies with midnight -</p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>&#8220;I&#8217;m gonna read you through Transitions lenses. I can do this all day, all night I promise you&#8221;.  </em></strong></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 style="text-align: justify;">Oh Whiplash !</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The Whitney Houston Hologram is unbelievable.  It&#8217;s almost like she&#8217;s coming direct from Heaven.  She is a side character which adds spice even as you ask  yourself why she is skyping in. Yes you have Divas and they are hilarious.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">At the 2:45 mark the shade begins to thicken quickly on Mary J&#8217;s Burger King Chicken Commercial. This is sublime.  Mary J goes off. but it hits the fan when Toni says :</p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>&#8220;she should have just tap danced for watermelon slices in front of the NAACP Headquarters.&#8221;</em></strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><object width="500" height="284" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/Q6OJBjCJLx4?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed width="500" height="284" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/Q6OJBjCJLx4?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" allowFullScreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" /></object></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">It really shows you how intense the shade is when Mary J&#8217;s hair flips to the other side at the 3:49 mark. wow they really take the time to put in a lot of small details which show you how much fun they&#8217;re having doing this.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>It&#8217;s so refreshing when Mary J snaps back at Toni and says</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>&#8220;Wat&#8217;n nobody even talking to you Toni Broketon. I&#8217;m looking at you right now. you can&#8217;t afford a backdrop. You sitting there in front of a blank ass screen. Like you are a PSA for Flop Insurance.&#8221; </em></p>
</blockquote>
<h1 style="text-align: justify;">BANG !</h1>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The brilliant young producers should surely get at least a job working for some film company;  after this circulates a bit.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This is written and performed mostly by Men from what we can tell. It&#8217;s just enough Diva for me. I wonder what Patty, Aretha, Dion, Mariah, Janet, Beyonce, Rihanna, Chaka, Toni, Diana, Fantasia, Nicki, Christina, Queen B and Lady Gaga have to say about the parodies of themselves.</p>
<blockquote>
<h2>You will see other episodes of this here very soon.</h2>
</blockquote>
