		<title>Michigan Why Do You want to Be Mean, instead of Healthy and GREEN ?</title>
		<link>http://badgals-radio.com/michigan-why-do-you-want-to-be-mean-instead-of-healthy-and-green</link>
		<comments>http://badgals-radio.com/michigan-why-do-you-want-to-be-mean-instead-of-healthy-and-green#comments</comments>
