<p style="text-align: justify;">Jr Gong and B Real cooked up some smokin riddims. The basis for this tune is simple; which is why we think this is going to burn up the airwaves, for a long time to come. It&#8217;s clean enough to make the Reggae and HipHop show charts on Internet and maybe Public Radio.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We&#8217;re undecided about commercial charts at this point. mostly because it&#8217;s an election year and things are different. The subject matter could make it a cult favorite. Just as the riddim could make it a dancehall staple for years to come. it&#8217;s hard to decide. but one thing is certain &#8211; this is a hit. no doubt, a bonified cross over hit.</p>
