		<link>http://badgals-radio.com/when-will-green-finally-put-red-back-in-the-black</link>
		<comments>http://badgals-radio.com/when-will-green-finally-put-red-back-in-the-black#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 21 Apr 2012 06:47:49 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Reality</dc:creator>
